{"tid":562540,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[經典重現] 發現六國論都幾似講緊香港部份建制派同反對派","createTime":"2018-02-16T04:35:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-16T04:35:46.000Z","uid":31637,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"9762537a185014dbb791da2d853d0e03751817b5","tid":562540,"uid":31637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-16T04:35:46.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www2.hkedcity.net/sch_files/a/tpy/tpy-syl/public_html/chinlang1.13.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkedcity.net%2Fsch_files%2Fa%2Ftpy%2Ftpy-syl%2Fpublic_html%2Fchinlang1.13.htm&d=Odt83XHNhBZYezGTnddDE8VakpCEQgWe3bOYm8oES40%3D&h=0e7d3e72\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkedcity.net/sch_files/a/tpy/tpy-syl/public_html/chinlang1.13.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n六國滅亡的原因：<br />\n<br />\n1.賂秦者之亡：(韓、魏、楚) <span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;---地產黨,鄉紳黨等等</span><br />\n<br />\na)賂秦力虧，自招滅亡。<br />\n<br />\nb)秦國受賂則國力日益強，大賂秦者則日漸衰弱。<br />\n<br />\n3.不賂秦者：<br />\n<br />\na)個別原因：<br />\n<br />\n1)齊：助秦不助五國。 <span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;---投建制焦土派</span><br />\n<br />\n2)燕：用荆軻刺秦王失敗。 <span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;---掟磚港獨派</span><br />\n<br />\n3)趙：殺良將李牧，自毀抗秦力量。 <span style=\"color: red;\">&lt;---屈鬼黨泛民</span><br />\n<br />\nb)    共同原因：<br />\n<br />\n不賂者因賂秦者(韓、魏、楚)而失去強緩，最後相繼滅亡。"}]}